Import it anytime by pasting into LocalStorage or use /import (coming soon).`;
            }
            
            // Check for garden-related keywords
            const keywords = {
                water: "üíß Watering is an art! It depends on your soil and plants. How often are you currently watering, and do you check if the soil is dry first?",
                sun: "‚òÄÔ∏è Sunlight is energy for plants. Most veggies need 6-8 hours. Do you know which parts of your garden get the most sun?",
